nodes.text: A Stormtrooper Commander was assigned to assist the Grand Inquisitor in hunting down the Spectres, who were protecting the fugitive Tseebo. Alongside the Inquisitor, the Stormtrooper Commander led a task force of stormtroopers to PM-1203 as its squad leader.
The Stormtrooper Commander on PM-1203 is voiced by Matthew Wood in "Gathering Forces," the ninth episode of Star Wars Rebels Season One.
